  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Westerlands.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"The westerlands and the location of Sarsfield\"><img alt=\"The westerlands and the location of Sarsfield\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7f/The_Westerlands.png/400px-The_Westerlands.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"444\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7f/The_Westerlands.png/600px-The_Westerlands.png 1.5x, /images/7/7f/The_Westerlands.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 44.4%; left: 46.7%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -6px; top: -6px; width: 12px; font-size: 12px;\"><img alt=\"The westerlands and the location of Sarsfield\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Sarsfield\" width=\"12\" height=\"12\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/18px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/24px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size: 100%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: -6.5em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\"><b>Sarsfield</b></span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">The <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a> and the location of Sarsfield\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><table>\n\n<tbody><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Sarsfield</b> is the seat of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Sarsfield\" title=\"House Sarsfield\">House Sarsfield</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a>. It is situated along the <a href=\"/index.php/River_Road\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"River Road\">River Road</a>, northeast of <a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a> and southwest of the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Tooth\" title=\"Golden Tooth\">Golden Tooth</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sarsfield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sarsfield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Sarsfield's mounted archers are part of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a>'s host which marches to the <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Riverrun\" title=\"Siege of Riverrun\">siege of Riverrun</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sarsfield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Map_of_the_South\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Map of the South\">Map of the South</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_27\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 27\">Chapter 27</a>, Jaime III.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible uncollapsed navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Region_Westerlands\" title=\"Template:Region Westerlands\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:Region_Westerlands&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:Region Westerlands (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:Region_Westerlands&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transpar